1. *Ubrzo* se svi sastali u parku. (They all soon met in the park.)
2. On je *ubrzo* došao do rezultata. (He soon came to the result.)
3. *Ubrzano* je trčao prema vratima. (He was running quickly towards the door.)
4. *Ubrzano* je stigla do škole. (She arrived quickly to the school.)
5. *Ubrzano* se razvio tehnološki napredak. (The technological progress developed quickly.)